rComments: Professor Guadagnolo gives awesome lectures; I was never bored. Make sure to attend class and participate in discussions as both are worth a big chunk of your grade. Mulitple small assignments; have to keep up with the readings. Not a super easy course; be prepared to put in the time for readings and assignments.

Dan is an extremely passionate and interesting lecturer (and person, it seems). His class has been one of the highlights of my History minor and I hope he comes back to teach more courses! The course itself was very engaging and interesting. He is a really funny and nice guy so don't be afraid to go up and talk to him about your work. He's awesome.
